subsidizers.translation:
subsidizer
n.
subsidize的变形
subsidize
['sʌbsidaiz]
vt.
发给…补助金(或津贴)；资助：
Soldiers are subsidized in our country .
在我国军人享受津贴待遇。
用酬金取得…的帮助：
to subsidize the border guards for smoothly leaving
为顺利出境而买通边防哨卡
收买，贿赂拉拢；向…行贿：
He was arrested for subsidizing the chief procurator.
他因向检察长行贿而被警方拘捕。
变形：
vt.
subsidized
. subsidizing
